### Basal Metabolic Rate

The *Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR)* needs four parameters

* *height* in centimers
* *weight* in kilograms
* *age* in years
* *gender* *male* or *female*

As the result you get an object in *basalMetabolicRate* containing the result of
